{
  "message": "feat(conformance): add FP-P2D-022 DataFrame constructor list-like shape taxonomy packet\n\nAdd a new conformance packet FP-P2D-022 covering DataFrame constructor\nlist-like input shape taxonomy with 14 fixture variants exercising\nstrict and hardened mode behavior:\n\nFixture Coverage:\n- default_column_labels_three_strict: basic 3-row matrix with auto-generated\n  column labels\n- empty_columns_nonempty_rows_error_hardened: error path when columns are\n  empty but rows are provided\n- empty_rows_nonempty_index_error_strict: error path for empty rows with\n  non-empty index specification\n- explicit_columns_empty_rows_hardened: empty data with explicit column\n  headers in hardened mode\n- float_and_int_columns_hardened: mixed float/int column dtype handling\n- index_length_mismatch_large_hardened: large index vs data length mismatch\n  error detection\n- missing_matrix_rows_error_strict: strict error when matrix rows are missing\n- null_fill_determinism_hardened: deterministic null padding behavior\n- ragged_three_rows_null_padding_hardened: ragged row lengths with null fill\n- ragged_with_explicit_columns_and_index_strict: ragged rows combined with\n  explicit column/index specification\n- row_width_exceeds_columns_by_two_strict: strict error when row width\n  exceeds declared column count\n- shape_square_strict: square matrix shape validation\n- shape_wide_rectangular_hardened: wide rectangular matrix handling\n- utf8_index_and_values_strict: UTF-8 index labels and cell values\n\nCode Changes (lib.rs):\n- Reformat max_row_width computation chain for readability (no logic change)\n- Add packet_filter_runs_constructor_shape_taxonomy_packet test that validates\n  FP-P2D-022 loads all 14+ fixtures and passes in FixtureExpected oracle mode\n\nPacket Artifacts (artifacts/phase2c/FP-P2D-022/):\n- contract_table.md: input/output contracts and edge-case matrix\n- fixture_manifest.json: fixture registry with mode and category metadata\n- legacy_anchor_map.md: mapping to upstream pandas test anchors\n- parity_gate.yaml: automated parity gate configuration\n- risk_note.md: risk surface analysis for list-like constructor paths\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
